title: Designing Ireland S01E01 PDTV.x264-TVCUK.mp4
description:
A landmark four-part series that takes viewers to the heart of Irish design: from beautifully crafted furniture to award-winning buildings to cutting-edge product design. Award-winning architect Angela Brady, OBE and respected design writer Dr Sandra O'Connell celebrate the very best of Irish design and meet the Irish designers, makers and architects whose work is creating waves locally, nationally and internationally.




Designing Ireland - Series 1, Episode 1


Identity

Angela and Sandra look back at Irish design, past and present, as they trace the beginnings of the modern Irish design.



Original Air Date: 05-Nov-2015
